🚀 Mirage Master Helper v8.0 - [FINAL STABLE]
The Ultimate Android Identity Management & Stealth Network Engine.

Welcome to the biggest update of the Mirage Master Helper! Version 8.0 brings an entirely rewritten core engine designed for Enterprise-Grade Network Privacy, Deep System Cleaning, and Seamless App Session Switching.

Whether you are managing multiple accounts or routing specific apps through secure proxies, v8.0 handles it flawlessly at the kernel level.

🌟 Key Features & User Benefits
🛡️ 1. Bulletproof Proxy Engine (Zero IP Leaks)
Per-App Stealth Routing: Select specific apps to route through your SOCKS5 proxy while the rest of your phone uses normal internet.

Kernel-Level Firewall (iptables): Completely re-engineered routing using advanced fwmark and iptables. Your original IP (both IPv4 and IPv6) is strictly locked out from leaking.

Smart Proxy Validation: Built-in intelligent SOCKS5 checker that actively verifies true internet data flow before connecting, ensuring you never get stuck on a "Dead" connection.

🧹 2. Deep Wipe & Anti-Tracking
Aggressive App Cleaning: One-tap complete wipe of targeted apps. It doesn't just clear data; it hunts down and destroys deep code_cache, hidden app_webview traces, and native memory buffers.

Universal AdID Reset: Automatically resets Google Advertising ID traces globally to protect your device identity footprint.

♻️ 3. Seamless Session Switcher (Insta-Login Saver)
Device-Encrypted (DE) Backup Support: Switching accounts on strict apps (like Instagram) will no longer log you out! The new engine backs up and restores encrypted Keystore paths perfectly.

Automated Permissions Fix: Automatically restores proper SELinux contexts and UID ownerships during session restores, preventing mysterious app crashes.

💾 4. Full Export & Import (SD Card Support)
Portable Identities: Easily export your entire session ecosystem (including JSON identity profiles and app data) directly to your external SD Card (/sdcard/MirageBackups).

Quick Migration: Import entire sessions back into the secure internal storage with a single tap.
